Use OpenCV¶

In [1]:
import cv2

Read an Image¶

In [2]:
# i tng 'img' cha thng tin nh
img = cv2.imread('1.jpg')

Display an Image¶

Use CV2

In [3]:
# cv2.imshow(window_name, image)
cv2.imshow('Beautiful', img)
cv2.waitKey(0)
Out[3]:
-1

Chy lnh ny s c mt ca s xut hin:

Hm waitKey(0) l hm ch khng cho thot ca s lp tc m phi ngi dng nhn phm bt k thot.

Use matplotlib¶

In [4]:

In [5]:

CV2 mc nh c nh mu theo th l BGR (l blue, green v red) nn nh c mu hi xanh.

V vy ta phi vit th ny:
